    "Training Time: Efficiently condensed to just over two minutes per epoch, the complete training duration is approximately eleven hours, exemplifying the model's efficient learning process. 9.",
    "Inference Time: An impressive inference speed of 50 ms is achieved, enabling rapid object detection crucial for real-time application scenarios.As mentioned before, the novel algorithm was trained and tested using the COCO dataset to enhance its performance at each stage.",
